column6: Description
Not even the freezing depths of winter can slow you down. The blood of your foes will flow as freely as you
The Karui gods have blessed you with fire. Summon the aid of your ancestors, and set the battlefield aflame.
The more you hurt, the more you hurt! Let rage fuel each swing of your weapon.
Shock your enemies into submission, or set them alight, or even freeze them in place. The power of the elements is at your fingertips!
Drain your enemy's life force with Chaos damage, or weaken them with debilitating curses. A master of the Dark Arts.
Raise zombies from the bodies of your defeated foes, or use their remains to empower your army.
Speed and damage are your two allies as you enter battle, annihilate your foes, and escape before they have a chance to respond
Supplement your skills with potent potables. Never be without a full flask!
Stand back lure your enemies wander into deluge of whistling arrows. If they can't reach you, they can't beat you.
Whether by spell or by weapon, punish heretics with the full might of the elements!
Protect your thoughts with masses of mana, and call forth the power of the Ancestors with an army of Totems.
Lend aid to your allies through a multitude of powerful auras, but beware: a lonely Guardian is a dead Guardian.
Crush your foes with the might of two-handed weapons. The best defense is a good offense!
Whether you're wielding a shield or any combination of weapons, you're ready to tackle any challenge. The key to victory is simply to outlast.
Mix might with mettle, and take down the strongest foes you come across. The bigger they are, the harder they fall.
Use every trick in the book to debilitate your foes and keep them from ever getting close to you.
Master the art of explosives! A field of carefully laid traps and mines can bring down even the toughest of foes.
Get the jump on your enemies and obliterate them with critical strikes before they even know what is happening.

Killer Frost is naturally attuned to the power of primordial magic. Able to summon totems, releasing a large pulse of freezing air, he can stand at a safe distance and vanquish any of Wraeclast's monsters with ease.

People say when she arrived on this damned isle, that she was just a girl. Fate had different plans for her when she accidentally fell into a portal connecting to the Ancient Vaal Era. She was exposed to the Vaal Pyramid's power of fire, and since then fire has become her. Fire kills...and also gives anew.
His ancestors were once in the service of an Ancient Vaal Assassination Cult, the skills of assassination flows in his blood. A master at traps, he savours his victory... from the shadows.

Use dominating blow to cause melee damage, applying a debuff to an enemy. If you kill the enemy within the debuff duration, the enemy will turn into a sentinel that will fight for you. When you hit an unique enemy you also have a chance to summon a sentinel.

Fire arrows towards the sky, they will land at the targeted location, dealing damage to enemies that are hit and creating a spore where they landed. Every spore does chaos damage over time to nearby enemies and reduce their movement speed. After a short delay, the spores explode, dealing area of effect damage.

Ancestral Warchief was always a starting skill for players, you can let your totem be both your vanguard and bodyguard. Now we have the powerful Vaal version of this skill at our disposal, be it a single enemy or multiple packs of enemies, neither can stand against the power of Vaal Ancestral Warchief.

Use the newly-reworked Ice Spear skill to unleash deadly freezing projectiles at enemies. Attain the new Winter Orb skill at later levels to channel an icy orb above your character that rapidly lobs projectile explosions at nearby enemies.
Use the new Brand skills to attach damaging effects to enemies. Storm Brand zaps nearby enemies with lightning damage, detaching and re-attaching to another enemy if it's recipient dies.
Slice your enemies with a flurry of blades that orbit you at high speeds.
Inflict the new Soulrend skill on enemies with deadly chaos damage over time projectiles weaving across the battlefield. Apply curses with the new Bane skill to bring down bosses and tougher enemies.
Devastate the battlefield with the new Divine Ire skill, charging up damage from nearby enemies to inflict a beam of destructive energy.
Experiment with the new self-cast spell supports with this Self-Cast Lightning Witch build. Use the new Unleash support gem with Spark to saturate the battlefield with deadly lightning projectiles.
Wield the destructive powers of the Void and watch as enemies melt away.
Rain death across your enemies, and entangle them in toxic vines.
Overwhelm enemies with your martial prowess. Leave no one standing!
Shatter the earth and all who stand on it with ground-shaking blows.
Draw upon the power of the divine as you purify Wraeclast once and for all.
Bring about the end of the world for all who stand against you.
Strike hard and fast at enemies with the new Chain Strike skill. Enrage against your foes and bring them to the ground.
Use superior martial ability to bring a typhoon of destruction with the new Bladestorm skill. Switch stances with the new Blood and Sand skill gem to anticipate your foes and outmatch them.
Become a whirlwind of death with the reworked Cyclone skill. Strike at enemies with unrelenting attacks and channel destructive energies with the Cast While Channeling support gem.
Use devastating explosives to control the battlefield with newly-reworked Mine skills. Detonate large mine clusters for overwhelming explosve power.

Overwhelm enemies with an undead army with the revamped Summoner Mechanics. Use powerful minions, summon the dreaded Carrion Golem, and make your creatures Defensive or Aggressive as a master of the dead.
Afflict enemies and watch them deteriorate with the new Poison gems. Apply the new deadly poisons to seal your enemies' fate, then escape away with the new Elusive mechanic.
Control the battlefield with devastating explosive mines. Use Arc Mines to defeat large groups of enemies, and use Pyroclast Mines to launch mortar rain on boss enemies.
Burn foes to ashes with this fiery bow Chieftain build. Begin with simple fire attacks then pick up a bow to set foes alight with waves of Burning Arrows.
Set up powerful Ballistas that rain powerful artillery on enemies. Build powerful Ballista totems to fight enemies from afar while you avoid dangerous foes.
Taunt enemies and overwhelm them with powerful new warcry skills. Power yourself up or intimidate your foes as you pulverize them with Earthshatter.
Chill enemies to their bones with the new Winter Brand skill. Conjure deadly vortexes to slow enemies while your Brands batter foes to their death.
Make the earth tremble and boil with devastating new slam skills. Bring your foes to their knees with the titanic strength of Tectonic Slam.

Transform your energy shield into a lightning blade and cover the screen in spinning copies of it.
Poisons enemies with chaos filled bottles melting their life pools away.
Uses Spark to turn Tornado into a lightning storm that mows down enemies.
Channel the power of lightning to pulverize your foes.
Call upon holy flames from the heavens to smite your foes.
Concentrate the essence of winter into your arrow tips.
Surprise your foes with deadly shards of ice.
Summon an army of toxic skeletons, corroding everything in your path.
Bend the earth to your will, churning the ground to engulf your foes.
Channel lightning from the heavens itself, devastating all that is around you.
Conjour statues that sweeps away all foes with a deadly and swift frozen slash.
Crack open the lands and releash its pent up fury, engulfing enemies in an explosion of magma.
Chill enemies to their bones with the new Winter Brand skill. Conjure deadly vortexes to slow enemies while your Brands batter foes to their death.
